    <item>
      <title>耶伦宣称美国经济已实现软着陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/yellen-declares-us-economy-has-achieved-soft-landing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周五宣布，美国经济已经实现了期待已久的软着陆，这是历史上不寻常的事件，高通胀得到抑制，但没有严重损害劳动力市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/yellen-declares-us-economy-has-achieved-soft-landing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一量子呼吁巴拿马防止已关闭矿场发生暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/first-quantum-expresses-concern-ahead-of-protest-at-panama-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第一量子矿业有限公司 (First Quantum Minerals Ltd.) 呼吁安全部队防止其已关闭的巴拿马铜矿发生骚乱，因为抗议者计划在该矿场附近示威。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/first-quantum-expresses-concern-ahead-of-protest-at-panama-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国服务业数据疲弱推升美联储降息押注，金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/gold-falls-as-us-jobs-data-curbs-bets-on-early-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业指标低于预期，美国国债收益率走低，金价上涨，增强了美联储今年迅速降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/gold-falls-as-us-jobs-data-curbs-bets-on-early-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 13:47:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于数据影响收益率，债券交易商对 2024 年美联储降息持坚定态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/treasuries-plunge-as-job-creation-pace-dims-wagers-on-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管周五公布的一系列就业和服务业数据令收益率大幅下滑，但国债交易员仍坚定押注美联储将在 2024 年大幅降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/treasuries-plunge-as-job-creation-pace-dims-wagers-on-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 13:37:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布后，欧洲股市录得十月份以来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/european-stocks-resume-their-slump-ahead-of-key-us-jobs-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的美国就业数据强化了美国经济软着陆的理由，削弱了提前降息的前景，欧洲股市录得自 10 月份以来最差的单周表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/european-stocks-resume-their-slump-ahead-of-key-us-jobs-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 08:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
